{"tid":1290513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「台灣外交部長」獲邀赴歐演說 給中國新大使重重一擊！","createTime":"2019-07-06T13:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T01:16:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69b6e169a1d98e951d5c502c7f1144aecd718287","tid":1290513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"「台灣外交部長」獲邀赴歐演說 給中國新大使重重一擊！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2844325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2844325&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=dd77cf3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2844325&h=ad23b488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2844325</a>"},{"pid":"052d94d16e2a0cbb3409f78a399054fc2059dde4","tid":1290513,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:50:03.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕外交部長吳釗燮應丹麥前總理、北約前秘書長拉斯穆森（Anders Fogh Rasmussen）邀請，上月底出席在在丹麥哥本哈根舉辦的「2019民主高峰會」，吳釗燮並以「中華民國（台灣）」外交部長的頭銜在會中發表演講，主辦的民主聯盟基金會會後在推特公布吳釗燮和其他與會者照片，同時加上我國旗，標註「the Foreign Minister of #Taiwan」。在此同時，中國新任駐丹麥大使馮鐵5月上任，拉斯穆森邀請吳釗燮到丹麥演說，被視為給中國外交部重重一擊！<br />\n<br />\n本報日前報導，吳釗燮出席這場民主高峰會（2019 Copenhagen Democracy Summit），以「中華民國（台灣）」外交部長的頭銜演說。拉斯穆森隨後在推特貼出兩人合照，表示他非常榮幸邀請「台灣的外交部長」（the Foreign Minister of #Taiwan）。吳釗燮演說中指出，儘管台灣是非常年輕的民主政體，但已經透過總統選舉和平的經歷3次政權轉移，台灣在亞洲無論是政治、媒體或言論自由的排名都名列前茅，但台灣的民主仍舊面臨不少挑戰。"},{"pid":"da650ec3f81d0895ee2f88fed7184f6bc1002781","tid":1290513,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"《上報》報導，拉斯穆森長期關注民主議題，這次主動邀請吳釗燮，向國際社會發聲，說明台灣的民主進程及面臨中國的威脅。因我國與歐洲各國無正式外交關係，加上中國可能打壓，吳釗燮此次行程如以往低調，外交部未發布新聞稿，會後才推文。<br />\n報導提到，主辦的基金會不僅在會議文件上以「中華民國（台灣）外交部長（Minister of Foreign Affairs, Republic of China（Taiwan））」介紹吳釗燮，臉書上也全程直播吳釗燮演說，拉斯穆森和基金會也在推特上公布吳釗燮和與會者的照片，並標註我國國旗。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述外交人士說法，吳釗燮以外長身分前往丹麥，我方與基金會以受分享台灣民主經驗為由，最後說服了丹麥政府，可說是不可為而為之的做法。而這對於甫由中國外交部港澳台司長轉任丹麥的中國大使馮鐵，可說是顏面無光，重擊中國外交部。<br />\n<br />\n拉斯穆森對於民主政體對抗外來干預相當重視，自北約秘書長職位卸任後，2017年創立「民主聯盟基金會（Alliance of Democracies Foundation）」，其中有常態運作的「民主運動計劃（The Campaign for Democracy）及每年舉辦「哥本哈根民主高峰會」，以支持國際民主運動及倡議人士。"},{"pid":"02a2a9bcfd592f043cc9219606d5edeace044a9b","tid":1290513,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"歐洲都咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a861cb38fba0492d6de7b0ac2f6e175f7bafd38d","tid":1290513,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"中華民國萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4bb5cd1a7d0cefcc6e17c0bc416fa6dafb06df","tid":1290513,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><del>中華民國</del>萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣萬歲"},{"pid":"06cd55f78ef6449cda5d1c696a72593114f77503","tid":1290513,"uid":114032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"鬼牌論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f57c6b7df5d86b83eb0fdb0eee2c3cc9e00d585","tid":1290513,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d443f7911398de9d0cc4177864fc6609fff84b5","tid":1290513,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"玩到咁大，唔怕俾人制裁？"},{"pid":"4bd21d2e7c27179faa888ca5509b9699768cdafa","tid":1290513,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"肯定係中國太強大, 全世界都紅眼, 一齊杯葛佢<br />\n身為中國人, 真係睇唔撚過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強烈要求祖國核平台灣, 以示淫威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5dd241b5ea52a18762c09f87b4ef3e2375092d","tid":1290513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed7b5934bd8d845ef3d22c22d56f8812e72cc71","tid":1290513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}